high_descs: Turn around and go across the room. Face the counter to the left.
Pick up the ladle on the right side of the counter.
Hold the ladle and take a step to the left.
Place the ladle in the bowl on the left side of the counter.
Pick up the bowl from the counter.
Carry the bowl and turn left and right around the counter.
Open the bottom right cabinet and place the bowl and ladle inside.
anns.task_desc: Move a bowl and ladle to a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter space beside the stove.
Pick up the ladle from the counter.
Re-position to the left and face the bowl on the counter.
Place the ladle inside of the bowl on the counter.
Pick up the bowl.
Turn left then turn right and walk to the cabinets.
Place the bowl in the rightmost cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a ladle in it inside of the cabinet.

high_descs: Walk to the edge of the kitchen counter on your left.
Grab the spoon off the counter.
Walk in front of the cup.
Place the spoon in the cup.
Grab the cup with the spoon in it.
Walk to the cabinets near the stove.
Place the cup in the bottom right cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup and spoon away in a cabinet.
